data.description: BEAUTIFUL home in the subdivision of Baker Estates. This home is located on a corner lot, with a long porch to sit and enjoy the outdoors. The kitchen is EQUIPPED with plenty of WOOD CABINETS for storage and a 5-burner GAS STOVE. THE LIVING ROOM and DEN are open with NEW VINYL PLANK FLOORING (2023), two large BAY WINDOWS and a built-in bookshelf. Separate DINING ROOM with space for a very large dining room table and China cabinet. You will also find an ENORMOUS MASTER BEDROOM EN-SUITE with two walk-in closets and a sitting area to unwind and relax. This home has NEW FLOORING, a NEW HOT WATER HEATER, GAS STOVE/RANGE and NEW HVAC replaced in 2018. Home also features a METAL ROOF, a COVERED PATIO, and a HUGE yard for entertaining. Make your appointment today to see this SPACIOUS HOME.
